name: Bonnie
mes:

name: Bonnie
mes:

Foot fetish can be a powerful distraction. I've done some research on similar techniques - it's said that skillful use of feet can be incredibly hypnotic if used right. The soft touch, the gentle caress... It's easy to lose focus."

Imagine your opponent's feet, so soft and inviting, slipping into your waistband, wrapping around your dick or toes. Such tempting thoughts can weaken anyone's resolve."
